    <title>EXPRESS: Supply chain risk and resolution: An empirical study of stock market reactions</title>
    <updated>2026-01-22T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Keno Theile, Christian Hofer, Vinod R. Singhal, Kai Hoberg</name>
