    <title>EXPRESS: The Implications of Retail Trade-ins on Sales, Returns, and Profitability: An Empirical Analysis of a Jewelry Trade-in Program</title>
    <updated>2026-01-06T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Necati Ertekin, Atalay Atasu, Vishal V. Agrawal</name>
